name: KissAnime-DTA
tagline: KissAnime DTA is a userscript that lets you display download links for all episodes on KissAnime so you can use DownThemAll! or similar tools to download them.
body:
### KissAnime DTA
KissAnime DTA is a userscript that lets you display download links for all episodes on KissAnime so you can use DownThemAll! or similar tools to download them.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
